The problem is that library &#39;g2c&#39; is not found.  Try editing &#39;setup.py&#39;  
in Cantera/python to remove this library if you don&#39;t need it, or to  
rename it.  It might be &#39;f2c&#39; on your system.  The linux configuration  
options are set up for RedHat linux, since that is all I have  
available.  It may be that Mandrake is different.

Numarray is not supported; Cantera uses Numeric only.


